Metadata-Version: 1.0
Name: Lavengro
Version: 1.1.8
Summary: Python Vocabulary Test Engine
Home-page: http://python.org/pypi/Lavengro
Author: Richard Harris
Author-email: richardharris@operamail.com
License: GNU General Public License
Description: Lavengro is a cross-platform, console-based vocabulary-test engine.  It
        uses text files as its tests. The tests themselves are created by
        you. It has a tutor mode, a test mode, and a CBT learning mode.
        There is also a bsd-quiz mode for nostalgia's sake.
        
Platform: any
